                            <comment id="17181347" author="edimitrova" created="Thu, 20 Aug 2020 17:18:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=brandon.williams&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;brandon.williams&quot;&gt;brandon.williams&lt;/a&gt;. Actually I wanted to confirm.... is this gonna be published with the new view of the web page before beta2 or not?&lt;br/&gt;
As if it is gonna be roll out with beta2, it needs to be changed to 4.0-beta2. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=lorina%40datastax.com&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;lorina@datastax.com&quot;&gt;lorina@datastax.com&lt;/a&gt;, can you advise, please?&lt;br/&gt;
