                            <comment id="17181359" author="michaelsembwever" created="Thu, 20 Aug 2020 18:01:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=e.dimitrova&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;e.dimitrova&quot;&gt;e.dimitrova&lt;/a&gt;, in cassandra-website there is a macro for the latest version, so changes like this don&apos;t have to be made:&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra-website/blob/master/src/_data/releases.yaml&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra-website/blob/master/src/_data/releases.yaml&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Something similar does exist for the in-tree docs (though I&apos;ve never used it):&lt;br/&gt;
